sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant TAS as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>TLS (optional)

    Note over User, DB: Flow 1: TrustyAI Model Explainability

    User->>Route: HTTPS/443<br/>Bearer Token
    Route->>KRBAC: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS 1.2+ (serving cert)
    KRBAC->>KRBAC: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(get verb on services)
    KRBAC->>TAS: HTTP/8080<br/>localhost (no TLS)
    TAS->>DB: TCP/configurable<br/>TLS (optional), Username/Password
    DB-->>TAS: Query Results
    TAS-->>KRBAC: Response
    KRBAC-->>Route: HTTPS Response
    Route-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over User, DB: Flow 2: KServe Payload Processing

    participant KServe as KServe<br/>InferenceService

    KServe->>TAS: HTTP/8080<br/>Payload Data (no auth)
    TAS->>DB: Store payload<br/>TCP, Credentials
    DB-->>TAS: ACK

    Note over User, DB: Flow 3: LM Evaluation Job Execution

    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant LMESCtrl as LMES Controller
    participant LMPod as LMEval Pod<br/>+ Driver Sidecar
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 / OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    User->>K8sAPI: Create LMEvalJob CR<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>LMESCtrl: Watch event
    LMESCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Pod<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>LMPod: Pod scheduled
    LMESCtrl->>LMPod: Status check<br/>HTTP/5000 (pod exec)
    LMPod->>HF: Download model/dataset<br/>HTTPS/443, API Token
    HF-->>LMPod: Model artifacts
    LMPod->>LMPod: Run evaluation
    LMPod->>S3: Upload results<br/>HTTPS/443, AWS IAM
    LMPod-->>LMESCtrl: Status update

    Note over User, DB: Flow 4: Guardrails Orchestration

    participant GORCHRoute as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant GKRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8432/TCP HTTPS
    participant Orch as Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator<br/>8032/TCP HTTPS
    participant Detector as Detector<br/>InferenceService
    participant GenSvc as Generation<br/>InferenceService

    User->>GORCHRoute: HTTPS/443<br/>Bearer Token
    GORCHRoute->>GKRBAC: HTTPS/8432<br/>TLS 1.2+
    GKRBAC->>GKRBAC: SubjectAccessReview
    GKRBAC->>Orch: HTTPS/8032<br/>TLS 1.2+ (serving cert)
    Orch->>Detector: Safety check<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, TLS 1.2+
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection result
    Orch->>GenSvc: Generate response<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, TLS 1.2+
    GenSvc-->>Orch: Generated output
    Orch->>Detector: Output check<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, TLS 1.2+
    Detector-->>Orch: Validation result
    Orch-->>GKRBAC: Safe response
    GKRBAC-->>GORCHRoute: HTTPS Response
    GORCHRoute-->>User: JSON Response
